cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for sentence classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses artificial neural networks, which are commonly used in machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with information retrieval and classification, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper mentions medical abstracts, which could involve computer vision techniques for medical imaging, making cs.CV (Computer Vision) a possible category as well.
